Speaker 2: I might cancel it out and you're good to go.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: No, you're all set.

Speaker 1: I'll cancel it out for you.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: No worries.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
